th america asia europe the middle east and africa the activities for europe the middle east and africa region emea are based in germany the company is also building a new research and development center located at the philadelphia naval shipyard known as the global innovation center in  axalta predecessor dupont published the first annual color popularity report the first in the industry to have extensive global data in one report the firm developed lab color equations an important component of modern color science it introduced the first waterborne electrical steel coating in the industry in the s productsedit among axaltas oldest products are standox and spies hecker cromax a waterbased product and the industrial paints napgard a powder coating for oil and gas pipeline companies and voltatex for electrical insulation were introduced in the s other products made by axalta include abcite alesta aquaec audurra centari challenger harmonized coating technologies imron and nason motorsportsedit jeff gordons cromaxsponsored car at texas motor speedway in  axalta currently sponsors the no  hendrick motorsports chevrolet ss of monster energy nascar cup series driver dale earnhardt jr and the no  jr motorsports chevrolet camaro of nascar xfinity series driver william byron previously the company sponsored fourtime series champion jeff gordons no  car a relationship which dated back to axaltas days as dupont and gordons first cup race in  as of the  brickyard  gordon has won three times in an axaltasponsored car all of which were in  during gordons career he ran variations of his axalta scheme to promote its brands such as cromax and standox on february   gordon was hired by axalta as a global business advisor in  axalta sponsored regan smiths jr motorsports camaro for the axalta faster tougher brighter  at phoenix international raceway the company has been a partner of the team since  axalta provides paint for the entire hendrick team along with three other nascar teams cam