 does business in  countries has nearly  employees and has more than  customers axalta traces its origins to the german firm herberts gmbh which began in  coating carriages before moving to automotive painting through later mergers the company became dupont performance coatings dpc part of the american dupont chemical empire and was rebranded as axalta coating systems after being purchased by the carlyle group in  axalta went public on the new york stock exchange in november of  and since then has become fully independent carlyle group exited their last ownership stake in axlta in  the company was the sponsor of fourtime nascar champion jeff gordon and the no  hendrick motorsports car a relationship which dated back to gordons first sprint cup series race in  axalta currently sponsors gordons former hms teammate dale earnhardt jr and the no  car contents  history  products  motorsports  references  external links historyedit the firms first products were developed in germany in  to protect carriages from the gravel of dirt roads in  the company created a quickdrying multicolor lacquer line for automotive painting operating as herberts gmbh the company grew under kurt herberts introducing the popular automobile finish standox in  in  herberts merged with dupont automotive finishes a transport coating systems technology company that had been started in  in wilmington delaware to form dpc in  the private equity firm the carlyle group announced its plans to purchase and discontinue dpc the carlyle group completed the sale in february  and founded axalta on november   the firm completed its ipo on the new york stock exchange nyse axta on january   axalta and chinese industrial coatings firm shanghai kinlita chemical formed a partnership to operate in china in april  berkshire hathaway invested  million in axalta coating systems in july  the firm acquired united paint and chemical corps automotive interior coatings business the company currently operates in north america south america asia europe the middle east and africa the activities for europe the middle east and africa region emea are based in germany the company is also building a new research and development center located at the philadelphia naval shipyard known as the global innovation center in  axalta predecessor dupont published the first annual color popularity report the first in the industry to have extensive global data in one report the firm developed lab color equations an important component of modern color science it introduced the first waterborne electrical steel coating in the industry in the s productsedit among axaltas oldest products are standox and spies hecker cromax a waterbased product and the industrial paints napgard a powder coating for oil and gas pipeline companies and voltatex for electrical insulation were introduced in the s other products made by axalta include abcite alesta aquaec audurra centari challenger harmonized coating technologies imron and nason motorsportsedit jeff gordons cromaxsponsored car at texas motor speedway in  axalta currently sponsors the no  hendrick motorsports chevrolet ss of monster energy nascar cup series driver dale earnhardt jr and the no  jr motorsports chevrolet camaro of nascar xfinity series driver william byron previously the company sponsored fourtime series champion jeff gordons no  car a relationship which dated back to axaltas days as dupont and gordons first cup race in  as of the  brickyard  gordon has won three times in an axaltasponsored car all of which were in  during gordons career he ran variations of his axalta scheme to promote its brands such as cromax and standox on february   gordon was hired by axalta as a global business advisor in  axalta sponsored regan smiths jr motorsports camaro for the axalta faster tougher brighter  at phoenix international raceway the company has been a partner of the team since  axalta provides paint for the entire hendrick team along with three other nascar teams camping world truck series kyle busch motorsports jr motorsports and the cup series stewarthaas racing indycar series team sarah fisher hartman racing also receives paint from axalta in addition to sponsoring gordon axalta sponsored the june cup series race at pocono raceway known as the axalta we paint winners  now known as the axalta presents the pocono  and the march xfinity series race at phoenix international raceway called the axalta faster tougher brighter  until  when dc solar replaced it as sponsor axalta also sponsors snocross team judnick motorsportpolaris racing who field riders ross martin and james johnstad in the amsoil championship snocross series the sponsorship lasts through  in  axalta became the title sponsor of the c team which competes in stock car brasil the team currently fields cars for júlio campos and gabriel casagrande through its spies hecker brand axalta provides paint for formula one team mercedes amg f mercedes team principal toto wolff stated the lightness of the paint allows the teams silver arrows cars to drop in weight assisting in performance referencesedit  a b pennell jay february   jeff gordon named axalta global business advisor foxsportscom retrieved february     company overview of axalta coating systems ltd bloomberg business february   retrieved february     a b c d axalta celebrates  years in the coatings industry european coatings journal january   retrieved july     kurt herberts the businessman standox retrieved july       the beginning of standox standox retrieved july     dupont colour and coating technologies dupont global retrieved july     the carlyle group to buy dupont performance coatings business for  billion the carlyle group august   retrieved february     mider zachary kaskey jack august   carlyle to buy dupont’s autopaint unit for  billion bloomberg lp retrieved february     axalta raised m in ipo  philadelphia business journal philadelphia business journal retrieved    axalta kinlita sign deal bodyshopbi